https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kEGYKOurGRH1qy6ONdxzJY8tXeb.jpg The movie "Abang Long Fadil 3" tells about the life of Fadil who received an offer from “NSS” (NATIONAL Secret Service) to be a professional spy in bringing down a largest group of thug ‘SSO” (Secret Society Organization) who led by “Chow Han” which with malicious intent to conquer the country of the archipelago. Agent Fadil is now cooperating with Agent Alice to bringing down the Chow Han's evil conspiracy, but things are getting complicated when “Yana” Fadil's ex-girlfriend interrupted NSS mission. Chow Han realizes that he has been spied on by the NSS, so he sends an assassin “King Cobra” to eliminate Fadil and Alice. Can Fadil complete this mission to save the country? Everything will be answered in "Abang Long Fadil 3" Abang Long Fadil 3
